.0, 540.0]]], "lines": ["そらろろ", "大丈夫か！？"]}, {"box": [274, 458, 344, 601], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20, "lines_coords": [[[322.0, 459.0], [343.0, 459.0], [344.0, 580.0], [323.0, 580.0]], [[298.0, 458.0], [318.0, 458.0], [321.0, 557.0], [301.0, 557.0]], [[274.0, 458.0], [294.0, 458.0], [297.0, 601.0], [277.0, 601.0]]], "lines": ["だから私自身、", "この傷には", "好きな男の子を、"]}, {"box": [79, 321, 120, 424], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20, "lines_coords": [[[98.0, 321.0], [120.0, 321.0], [120.0, 375.0], [98.0, 375.0]], [[79.0, 322.0], [96.0, 322.0], [96.0, 424.0], [79.0, 424.0]]], "lines": ["おーい", "降りてこい！"]}, {"box": [677, 630, 732, 727], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23, "lines_coords": [[[711.0, 632.0], [732.0, 632.0], [732.0, 725.0], [711.0, 725.0]], [[681.0, 630.0], [705.0, 631.0], [702.0, 727.0], [677.0, 726.0]]], "lines": ["うぎゃあ", "くくく～～"]}, {"box": [662, 758, 730, 896], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20, "lines_coords": [[[709.0, 758.0], [730.0, 758.0], [728.0, 896.0], [707.0, 896.0]], [[685.0, 760.0], [705.0, 760.0], [705.0, 877.0], [685.0, 877.0]], [[663.0, 759.0], [681.0, 759.0], [680.0, 881.0], [662.0, 881.0]]], "lines": ["実際、それ以来", "私の恋は必ず", "実ってるのよ。"]}, {"box": [374, 612, 413, 732], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16, "lines_coords": [[[396.0, 612.0], [412.0, 612.0], [412.0, 732.0], [396.0, 732.0]], [[374.0, 612.0], [390.0, 612.0], [390.0, 679.0], [374.0, 679.0]]], "lines": ["先生呼んでくる", "からな！！"]}, {"box": [260, 755, 346, 928], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17, "lines_coords": [[[328.0, 758.0], [344.0, 758.0], [344.0, 912.0], [328.0, 912.0]], [[306.0, 757.0], [322.0, 757.0], [322.0, 928.0], [306.0, 928.0]], [[283.0, 757.0], [300.0, 757.0], [300.0, 851.0], [283.0, 851.0]], [[260.0, 755.0], [280.0, 755.0], [280.0, 891.0], [260.0, 891.0]]], "lines": ["でも単なる偶然よ。", "そんなバワーなんて", "本当なわけ", "ないじゃない！"]}, {"box": [222, 765, 237, 809], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15, "lines_coords": [[[222.0, 765.0], [237.0, 765.0], [237.0, 809.0], [222.0, 809.0]]], "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box